WEBVTT

00:03.000 --> 00:04.920
我在找一个叫林肯·布伦斯的人
I'm looking for Lincoln Burrows

00:04.930 --> 00:06.850
杀了副总统哥哥的凶手
Man killed the VP's brother

00:06.860 --> 00:08.490
为什么你要这么急着找布伦斯?
Why you want to see him?

00:08.500 --> 00:09.690
因为他是我哥哥
He's my brother

00:09.700 --> 00:11.690
-我正在想办法救你出去  -这不可能
-I'll get you out.  -It's impossible

00:11.700 --> 00:13.350
除非监狱是你设计的
Not if you designed the place

00:13.360 --> 00:15.050
你见过设计蓝图了?
You've seen the blueprints

00:15.060 --> 00:16.250
何止见过
 Better than that

00:16.260 --> 00:18.850
我把他们纹在了身上
I've got 'em on me

00:18.860 --> 00:21.150
尼克·萨维恩 
Nick Savrinn

00:21.160 --> 00:23.350
从现在开始,你们两个死定了
As of now, both of you are dead

00:23.360 --> 00:24.650
我是贝利克
This is Bellick

00:24.660 --> 00:26.020
我们这区已经被突破了
Our wing has been breached

00:26.030 --> 00:27.550
玛丽莲  不要!
Marilyn, no!

00:27.560 --> 00:29.750
在监狱里
The chair isn't the only way

00:29.760 --> 00:31.350
行刑不一定非得通过电椅
to take a man's life in prison

00:31.360 --> 00:33.550
-你干什么?  -即使你父亲早就有麻烦了
-What are you doing?  -Your father's already in trouble

00:33.560 --> 00:34.790
我们谁也帮不了他
There's nothing we can do about it

00:34.800 --> 00:37.270
快点! 我第一次做P.I.
Come on!My first assignments on PI were up here

00:37.280 --> 00:39.690
就是来这里清理有毒物质
cleaning out toxic mould

00:39.700 --> 00:41.020
P.I.到不了那里
PI didn't go there

00:41.030 --> 00:42.790
我们也从不派犯人去那里
We'd never assign inmates to do that

00:42.800 --> 00:44.750
泰勒·罗伯特
Tyler, Robert

00:44.760 --> 00:48.100
这一定是你女儿喽
And this here must be your daughter

00:48.130 --> 00:50.150
这事算成了 我们不再需要他了
It's over. We don't need him

00:50.160 --> 00:52.760
那你也不能杀了他
You're not gonna kill him

00:56.560 --> 01:00.300
团队利益
One for the team

01:03.360 --> 01:04.920
十七天后
(Michael) 17 days from now

01:04.930 --> 01:08.530
我哥哥将坐上电椅
they strap my brother to an electric chair

01:09.700 --> 01:12.120
电压高达5万伏的电流将通过他身体
Send 50,000 volts coursing through his body

01:12.130 --> 01:15.520
只因为一个莫须有的罪名
for a crime he didn't commit

01:15.530 --> 01:19.360
我是来这里救他的
I'm here to make sure that doesn't happen

01:21.830 --> 01:24.590
我来狐狸河监狱 差不多3个星期了
I've been in Fox River nearly three weeks now

01:24.600 --> 01:27.920
这期间  我已可以从我狱室后面出来
In that time,I've got out the back of my cell

01:27.930 --> 01:32.750
进入到横贯监狱的旧蒸汽管道
and into the old steam pipes that run beneath the prison

01:32.760 --> 01:37.100
这些管道就是出口
Those pipes are our way out

01:37.400 --> 01:38.850
把这个地方
Think of this place

01:38.860 --> 01:41.290
当作是美国地图
like it's a map of the US

01:41.300 --> 01:45.030
我们的狱室在那 那是纽约市
Our cell over there, that's New York City

01:45.200 --> 01:47.790
而医务室  我们的出口 那是加州
The infirmary, our exit, that's California

01:47.800 --> 01:49.890
我们脚下连贯这两地的...
The pipes beneath us that connect the two...

01:49.900 --> 01:51.320
是66大道
Route 66

01:51.330 --> 01:53.050
66大道
Route 66

01:53.060 --> 01:54.320
我们自由之车的车票
Our ticket out of here

01:54.330 --> 01:56.420
我猜是晚上行动吧
I assume we're doing this at night?

01:56.430 --> 01:57.820
对
That's right

01:57.830 --> 02:00.520
这里看守这么严实 嫩鸡 而你的老哥
We're locked up, fish,and your boy

02:00.530 --> 02:01.850
被单独监禁
is in solitary

02:01.860 --> 02:04.090
我们这些鸟儿 怎样才可以飞出笼子
How we just gonna fly out of our cages

02:04.100 --> 02:05.550
到你的狱室去呢?
and  right into your cell

02:05.560 --> 02:07.150
怎么去纽约市?
right into New York City?

02:07.160 --> 02:08.720
不用到我狱室
You're not

02:08.730 --> 02:11.490
我们到时会在半路会合的
You're gonna meet me halfway

02:11.500 --> 02:13.050
在圣路易?
In St Louis

02:13.060 --> 02:15.350
66大道在那楼下底部穿过
Route 66 runs beneath that building

02:15.360 --> 02:17.190
在这些管道上面
It's the only building

02:17.200 --> 02:18.350
只有这座楼
sitting on top of those tunnels

02:18.360 --> 02:21.790
我们只要趁做P.I.的时候
All we gotta do is get in there, on PI

02:21.800 --> 02:23.390
在那里弄一个出口
and dig ourselves an on-ramp

02:23.400 --> 02:26.090
很快  我们就到医务室
Shortly after, we hit the infirmary

02:26.100 --> 02:27.850
到时我们就会逃出监狱了
Then we'll be outside those walls

02:27.860 --> 02:29.690
那边是什么地方?
What's in there?

02:29.700 --> 02:31.320
是一个旧储物室
It's an old storage room

02:31.330 --> 02:33.320
约翰可以利用他在这里的关系
John here can pull all the stringsThere's gotta be some actual work to be done in there for me

02:33.330 --> 02:35.020
没那么容易  嫩鸡
(John) It's not that easy, fish

02:35.030 --> 02:37.710
那是禁区
That's a restricted area

02:37.720 --> 02:39.790
我得要有个借口 骗过狱警
I gotta be able to justify it to the bulls

02:39.800 --> 02:42.400
让他们派我们去那里干活
There's gotta be some actual work to be done in there for me

02:42.410 --> 02:43.490
以便可以进去
to get in there

02:43.500 --> 02:44.490
你明白吗?
You follow?

02:44.500 --> 02:45.820
那你尽快找到
Then you better figure it out

02:45.830 --> 02:48.290
因为若我们进不了那房子
Cos if we don't get in that room

02:48.300 --> 02:49.590
我们就出不去
we're not getting out of here.

02:49.600 --> 02:52.990
好像有什么瞒着我?
I'm feeling kind of left out

02:53.000 --> 02:54.550
纽约?  加州?
New York? California?

02:54.560 --> 02:56.420
圣路易?
St Louis?

02:56.430 --> 02:57.420
我们在谈什么呢?
What are we discussing?

02:57.430 --> 02:58.990
棒球而已
We're talking baseball, actually

02:59.000 --> 03:00.520
是吗?
Oh.

03:00.530 --> 03:02.420
关于这个话题
Now, that's a subject

03:02.430 --> 03:03.450
我恰巧有点了解
 I know quite a bit about.

03:03.460 --> 03:04.450
真可惜
What a shame

03:04.460 --> 03:06.420
我们说完了
 The conversation's over

03:06.430 --> 03:07.350
真的吗?
Really, now

03:07.360 --> 03:08.720
你们就这样
That any way

03:08.730 --> 03:12.360
对待一个队友的吗?
 to treat a team-mate?

03:14.260 --> 03:16.190
不管你们愿意与否
I'm coming along on this endeavour

03:16.200 --> 03:18.650
我是一定要和你们纠缠下去了
whether you like it or not

03:18.660 --> 03:19.890
况且我还有
Cos I got

03:19.900 --> 03:24.200
一副好嗓子
 a hell of a singing voice otherwise

03:24.800 --> 03:26.790
我不会带上这个贱人的
I won't take that piece of crap along

03:26.800 --> 03:27.790
一定不会
I won't do it

03:27.800 --> 03:29.420
我也不会
Me neither

03:29.430 --> 03:31.090
我们不必带上他的
We won't have to

03:31.100 --> 03:34.730
他很快就不会缠住我们了
He'll be out of the picture soon enough

03:36.260 --> 03:38.550
州政府提供了2万5千美元保险金
The state provides $25,000 insurance

03:38.560 --> 03:42.220
加上从伊利诺斯州惩教署职员基金会的捐款
plus donations from the Corrections Officers' Foundation...

03:42.230 --> 03:46.930
监狱长  我现在不关心这个
That's the last thing on my mind right now, Warden

03:47.260 --> 03:48.650
你找到凶手了吗?
Do you know who killed him?

03:48.660 --> 03:51.250
我们掌握了些线索
We have some leads

03:51.260 --> 03:52.690
但我可以向你保证
But I can promise you this

03:52.700 --> 03:56.760
我们决不会让凶手逍遥法外的
We are not gonna rest until we find out what happened

03:57.160 --> 03:58.750
他的照片不见了
His pictures are missing

03:58.760 --> 04:03.630
这里有我们女儿的照片
He had a photo of our daughter in here

04:04.160 --> 04:05.320
不用担心
Not to worry

04:05.330 --> 04:08.160
我们会查清楚的
 We'll find them

04:08.460 --> 04:11.950
我求过他
I begged him

04:11.960 --> 04:14.050
让他不要干这份工作
not to take this job

04:14.060 --> 04:15.520
莎尔娜
Shauna

04:15.530 --> 04:18.260
我很抱歉
I am so sorry

04:19.660 --> 04:22.250
我陪你出去坐车
I'll walk you to your car

04:22.260 --> 04:24.450
队长
Captain

04:24.460 --> 04:26.550
我要和你谈一下
 need to speak with you for a second

04:26.560 --> 04:30.060
走廊见
I'll meet you in the hallway

04:30.200 --> 04:33.990
我要抓到那个龟孙子凶手
I want the son of a bitch who did this

04:34.000 --> 04:37.890
不管你用什么办法 你都要把他找出来
Now, you do whatever you need to do to find him

04:37.900 --> 04:43.300
明白吗?
You understand?

04:44.630 --> 04:49.400
这有5个箱子  过来帮一下忙好吗?
We got five boxes.Wanna give me a hand?

04:49.700 --> 04:53.050
维罗妮卡?
Veronica

04:53.060 --> 04:54.450
那电话是典型的恐吓手段
That phone call was  tactics scare

04:54.460 --> 04:55.950
他们就想吓一下你
That's they want.

04:55.960 --> 04:57.890
让我们望而生畏
They want to scare us from doing what they know we can do

04:57.900 --> 05:00.300
-那该怎么做?  -把他们曝光
-And what's that?  -Expose them

05:00.310 --> 05:03.020
多诺万小姐  这家伙又来烦你了吗?
Is this guy bothering you again?  Miss Donovan?

05:03.030 --> 05:05.120
不 卢卡斯 那个晚上是我的过错
No, Lukasz, the other night was my fault

05:05.130 --> 05:06.220
是个误会
It was a misunderstanding

05:06.230 --> 05:08.190
如果你有什么需要
OK. But if you need anything...

05:08.200 --> 05:09.090
相信我
Trust me

05:09.100 --> 05:12.020
要有事我第一个找你
you'll be the first person I call

05:12.030 --> 05:16.730
让我来
Here, let me

05:17.730 --> 05:19.550
这些箱子
Those boxes

05:19.560 --> 05:20.550
装着七年来
contain seven years

05:20.560 --> 05:22.250
上诉案件的档案
of criminal appellant work

05:22.260 --> 05:25.220
如果有先例
If there's a precedent in there somewhere

05:25.230 --> 05:28.320
可以使得林肯的死刑缓期执行 我们一定可以找到的
that can help us suspend Lincoln's execution,we're gonna find it

05:28.330 --> 05:30.190
你可以放到门边  卢卡斯
You can leave those by the door

05:30.200 --> 05:31.190
我会搬进去的
I'll bring them in

05:31.200 --> 05:32.350
好的
Oh, that's OK

05:32.360 --> 05:34.150
我这里有你的钥匙
I've got your key right here

05:34.160 --> 05:37.200
如果我不知情 还以为卢卡斯痴情于你呢
If I didn't know better,I'd say Lukasz was sweet on you.

05:37.210 --> 05:38.460
有趣
Very funny

06:28.490 --> 06:30.080
火
Fire

06:30.090 --> 06:31.080
什么?
 What?

06:31.090 --> 06:33.050
用火  我们把那地方烧为平地
Fire. We burn the place down

06:33.060 --> 06:34.650
对我们有什么用?
How's that gonna help us?

06:34.660 --> 06:36.200
几年前  礼拜堂发生大火
A few years ago, the chapel burnt down

06:36.210 --> 06:38.450
惩教署意识到
 and the DOC realised

06:38.460 --> 06:40.580
有一些有毒物质
they had some toxic issues

06:40.590 --> 06:43.110
像石棉  导火线
You know, asbestos, lead paint, you name it

06:43.120 --> 06:44.480
他们找不到承包商来清理
They couldn't find a contractor

06:44.490 --> 06:47.480
所以他们派狱犯来做
so they put the inmates on the job

06:47.490 --> 06:49.910
每次我们都在那呆5-6小时
We spent, like, five, six hours in there at a time

06:49.920 --> 06:51.450
但有一点比较好的是
But the good news is

06:51.460 --> 06:54.280
基本上没有守卫来巡逻
no guards came around almost at all

06:54.290 --> 06:57.210
你有办法带我们到那吗?
Can you get us in there?

06:57.220 --> 07:02.260
我仔细考虑过了
I've been doing a little, uh... thinking

07:06.120 --> 07:10.220
我要一张P.I.的工作证
I'm gonna need a PI card, aren't I?

07:10.490 --> 07:12.810
我是说
I mean

07:12.820 --> 07:14.610
那边是起事的地方 
that's where this whole thing is happening

07:14.620 --> 07:15.780
对吗?
isn't it?

07:15.790 --> 07:19.460
很快就给你
It's on its way

07:20.560 --> 07:22.180
你在敷衍我  对吗?
You're slow-walking me, aren't you?

07:22.190 --> 07:23.980
我为什么要这么做?
Why would I do that?

07:23.990 --> 07:25.610
你觉得贝利克会因狱警鲍勃那件事
You think Bellick's gonna pop me

07:25.620 --> 07:28.580
把我抓起来
for shanking that CO, Bob

07:28.590 --> 07:30.010
也许
Maybe

07:30.020 --> 07:32.180
你们会悄悄跑去告诉他  对吗?
you'll take a little walk, tell him for yourself?

07:32.190 --> 07:34.180
这样你们就可以摆脱我了
And I'll be out of here for good

07:34.190 --> 07:36.810
我有你的一些秘密
Well, I got news for you

07:36.820 --> 07:39.710
如果我因杀了鲍勃被抓起来
If I go down for killing Bob

07:39.720 --> 07:42.480
我不会就此作罢的
believe me,I'm gonna take a little walk of my own

07:42.490 --> 07:48.690
我会向他们禀明 你在你便池后面挖的洞
Tell 'em about that hole you got behind your toilet

07:49.820 --> 07:52.880
这么说来...
So...

07:52.890 --> 07:55.910
P.I.的工作证怎样?
How about that PI card?

07:55.920 --> 07:58.380
你还记得吗
I don't know if you remember

07:58.390 --> 08:01.080
在5年级的那个夏天
but that summer before fifth grade

08:01.090 --> 08:03.110
我和你住了两星期时
when I stayed with you a couple weeks

08:03.120 --> 08:07.590
你认为我打烂了玻璃咖啡桌
and you thought I broke your glass coffee table?

08:08.690 --> 08:10.880
你回家时  我否认了
And when you came home, I denied it

08:10.890 --> 08:13.680
但你告诉我
But you told me

08:13.690 --> 08:17.350
对咖啡桌你可以不在乎
you could care less about the coffee table

08:17.360 --> 08:19.310
但你不想我因此撒谎
you just didn't want me lying to you

08:19.320 --> 08:21.880
你说我说出事实
And you said I'd feel a lot better

08:21.890 --> 08:24.780
会觉得舒服点的
if I just told you the truth

08:24.790 --> 08:26.980
而你保证不会生气
And you promised not to be angry

08:26.990 --> 08:28.680
我记得
I remember

08:28.690 --> 08:31.680
对  是我打烂的
Well, I broke it

08:31.690 --> 08:36.060
我知道
I know

08:37.690 --> 08:39.780
如果你心里
You know, if there's anything

08:39.790 --> 08:41.410
有什么要说
that you want to get off your chest

08:41.420 --> 08:43.250
你可以告诉我
you can tell me

08:43.260 --> 08:45.710
我也保证不会生气
And I promise I won't get angry

08:45.720 --> 08:49.490
你想知道是不是我杀了那人
You want to know if I killed that guy

08:52.390 --> 08:59.480
当时我去那里  是想干点坏事
I, uh, went there planning to do something wrong

08:59.490 --> 09:01.480
但我没杀那个人
But I didn't kill that guy

09:01.490 --> 09:04.650
有人蓄意制造了我杀人的假象
Someone's working hard to make it look like I did

09:04.660 --> 09:08.980
不管怎样  仍有机会不用执行死刑
Anyway, there's a chance the execution may not happen

09:08.990 --> 09:10.480
什么?
What?

09:10.490 --> 09:12.080
维罗妮卡正在帮我
Veronica's working on my case

09:12.090 --> 09:13.610
今天有个记者来找我
and I got a reporter coming today

09:13.620 --> 09:16.510
她相信我是无辜的
who believes I'm innocent

09:16.520 --> 09:19.390
因此我还不用死
So I ain't dead yet

09:20.220 --> 09:23.650
LJ  看着我
LJ. Look at me

09:23.660 --> 09:26.750
你要有信念  孩子
You gotta have faith, kid

09:26.760 --> 09:31.490
坚持你的信念
Just have a little faith

09:37.990 --> 09:40.310
凯勒曼
Kellerman

09:40.320 --> 09:41.350
怎样了?
 Well?

09:41.360 --> 09:42.310
搞定了
Taken care of

09:42.320 --> 09:43.710
很好
Good

09:43.720 --> 09:45.610
现在进行第二步计划
Now move on to the second thing

09:45.620 --> 09:47.650
如果你见到我们在看的东西
If you could see what we're looking at...

09:47.660 --> 09:49.180
相信我  布伦斯会收到信息的
believe me,Burrows is gonna get the message

09:49.190 --> 09:52.280
这个你向我保证过了
Which is what you've assured me of before

09:52.290 --> 09:53.300
而这信息
Yet that message

09:53.310 --> 09:55.710
总是退回到发送者
keeps getting returned to sender

09:55.720 --> 09:58.380
现在着手第二步计划 然后向我报告
Now move on the second thing and report back

09:58.390 --> 10:00.410
我们现在去
We're headed there now

10:00.420 --> 10:02.650
你想得太多了
You're thinking too much

10:02.660 --> 10:06.090
是啊  但没办法
Yeah. God forbid

10:10.190 --> 10:12.180
在找到那个杀手之前
He'll toss every cell in this block

10:12.190 --> 10:13.950
他会将整个监狱挖地三尺
until he finds the killer

10:13.960 --> 10:15.250
他找到这里时
He tosses this one

10:15.260 --> 10:17.650
他会轻易找到后面那个洞的
he'll find the hole back there in a heartbeat

10:17.660 --> 10:20.110
我知道
I know

10:20.120 --> 10:21.410
我们得举报他
 We got to turn T-Bag in

10:21.420 --> 10:22.880
只有这样做才会停止搜查
That's the only way it'll stop

10:22.890 --> 10:25.590
我们若举报他 他会泄漏我们的秘密
 We turn him in, he'll talk

10:30.220 --> 10:35.190
看来无论怎样都是死路一条  对吗?
So we're screwed either way, aren't we?

10:38.890 --> 10:40.650
哪个房间?
Which one?

10:40.660 --> 10:41.750
就在那
Right there

10:41.760 --> 10:45.360
圣路易
St Louis

11:07.390 --> 11:09.910
你们来这干什么?!
What the hell are you doing here?

11:09.920 --> 11:11.680
清理工作队 我们以为这是储物室
Cleanup detail. We thought this was storage

11:11.690 --> 11:12.850
这像是个储物室吗
This look like storage to you?

11:12.860 --> 11:14.550
白痴 这是禁区
idiot  It's a restricted area

11:14.560 --> 11:16.010
