拥有很高的安全权限
Ones with high security clearance

12:02.260 --> 12:03.410
为什么是他?
 Why him?

12:03.420 --> 12:05.210
他们信得过他 
He can be trusted.

12:05.220 --> 12:06.210
怎么才可以成为囚犯理事?
 How does one become a trustee?

