只要三十年来没有不良记录
Have a spotless record for the last 30 years

12:07.390 --> 12:08.580
没不良记录
for the last 30 years

12:08.590 --> 12:10.110
我们的刑期加起来都没这么多
Pretty much counts us out

12:10.120 --> 12:12.110
看来得让他加入我们
Which means we've gotta get him on board

12:12.120 --> 12:17.120
算了吧 他不领任何人的情的
Forget it. The guy's a boy scout

12:21.860 --> 12:24.050
韦斯特莫兰德 先生?
Mr Westmoreland

12:24.060 --> 12:26.050
你好 迈克尔
Hey, Michael

12:26.060 --> 12:28.710
找到你的猫了吗?
You found your cat yet?

